commentary: Rubel Hossain to Panyangara, OUT that is brilliant fielding! He comes down the track and plays a checked drive towards mid-off and sets off for the single. Sabbir is the fielder and he quickly susses out that the keeper's end is the one to shy to, since Chigumbura was a little late to respond to Panyangara's call. He threw down the stumps direct, and Chiggy was out by a mile.
